high_descs: Pick up the green apple on the table.
Bring the apple to the fridge.
Chill the apple in the fridge.
Bring the chilled green apple to the table.
Put the apple on the table to the right of the salt.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled green apple on the table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk around to the far side of the white table
Pick up the green apple from the white table
Turn right and approach the fridge
Put the apple into the fridge and then remove it
Turn around and walk back to the white table
Put the apple on the table just right of the salt shaker
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled green apple on the white table

high_descs: Go to the far end of the table behind you.
Pick up the green apple on the table, next to the bread.
Turn around and go forward to the fridge.
Chill the apple in the fridge.
Turn around, go forward, then turn right to face the table.
Place the apple on the table, to the right of the salt.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple on the table.
